data.description: Looking for a beautiful and totally restored home in the perfect location? Look no further! This lovely 1.5 story, 3 bedroom, 2 bath condo was totally redone from the studs after Hurricane Laura. It is located at the end of a cul-de-sac right across from the community pool & clubhouse. It features a huge living room with vaulted ceiling & wood burning fireplace, kitchen with all appliances included (1 yr m/l), granite countertops & new laminate floors throughout. The downstairs master bedroom has a spacious single sink vanity and tub with overhead shower. Upstairs there are two more very large bedrooms, one of which has a huge walk-in closet, and another bath with single sink vanity, commode and walk-in shower.  The rear yard is fenced & has a 3 car carport with plenty of storage. This home is not just an amazing product but also an incredible experience you can have every day of your life! Plus, it's conveniently located near schools, shopping, medical facilities & I-10, so you don't have to worry about being far away from anything important. Don't miss out on this great opportunity. Call now to purchase this amazing home. You won't regret it.
